    public class PageElementRenderingResolver
extends Object
implements com.i2rd.domainmodel.resolver.DomainModelResolver
    PageElement rendering resolver. Renders PageElement content. This doesn't integrate caching information - it is not recommended that you use this class for that reason if it is possible to integrate in the normal page rendering process.
